* Test ChrHex and OrdHex functions with Unicode

$ENTRY Go {
  = <TestASCII>
    <TestUnicode>
    <TestEmoji>
    <TestRoundtrip>;
}

* Test ASCII range with hex
TestASCII {
  = <Prout 'Testing ASCII with hex:'>
    <Prout '  ChrHex 0x41 = ' <ChrHex '0x41'>>
    <Prout '  OrdHex A = ' <OrdHex 'A'>>
    <Prout '  ChrHex 0x61 = ' <ChrHex '0x61'>>
    <Prout '  OrdHex a = ' <OrdHex 'a'>>;
}

